	<br></br>
	The house and its accommodation are available for both corporate and private entertaining along with the surrounding parkland making the perfect backdrop for your own exclusive event. We have held events that range from meetings to weddings, clay pigeon shooting to team building, birthday parties to seminars and go-karting to B&Bâ€™s.
